  <img src="https://drive.google.com/uc?id=1ouaXzeEdR7KbKb7MQjK6r7k9UcxGIFIe" />
  <figcaption>Singapore - Jewel Changi International Airport</figcaption>
</figure>

<p>I was fortunate enough to walk around some beautiful natural trails around the country where I experienced a divine feeling, fresh oxygen and pure drinking water that comes out of the taps.</p>

